{"id":"807080270566211584","type":"text","timestamp":1769691725,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/807080270566211584","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":true,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://ohevoyev.tumblr.com/post/806642526651072512/state-officials-confirm-the-individual-died\">ohevoyev</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://ohevoyev.tumblr.com/post/806641099616681984/ice-shot-another-civilian-in-minneapolis-this\">ohevoyev</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a href=\"https://www.mprnews.org/live-updates\">ICE shot another civilian in minneapolis this morning</a></p></blockquote><p><a href=\"https://www.startribune.com/ice-raids-minnesota/601546426\">state officials confirm the individual has died</a> &hellip; ICE executed another person in broad daylight. and they&rsquo;ve begun escalating against protesters in the area.</p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"ohevoyev"},"post":{"id":"806641099616681984"}},{"blog":{"name":"ohevoyev"},"post":{"id":"806642526651072512"}}],"baseline_notes":3701,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}